```
This would allow a researcher to dump the contents of the analytics list as the application processes it, which might include merchant identifiers, event names, or UI state strings that could map out user behavior within the payment flow.

### [CONCLUSION]
This file is a "non-target." It is part of the Google Measurement framework embedded within the application. While it processes data, that data is limited to application telemetry.

